@PostHogSample.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5032

### Health
GET {{PostHogSample.Api_HostAddress}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

### Events - capture custom event
POST {{PostHogSample.Api_HostAddress}}/api/events/capture
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "distinctId": "user-123",
  "eventName": "order completed",
  "properties": {
    "order_id": "ord_456",
    "total": 99.5
  },
  "personPropertiesToSet": {
    "plan": "pro"
  }
}

### Events - identify user
POST {{PostHogSample.Api_HostAddress}}/api/events/identify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "distinctId": "user-123",
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "name": "Demo User",
  "personPropertiesToSetOnce": {
    "signup_source": "sample-api"
  }
}

### Events - demo product viewed
POST {{PostHogSample.Api_HostAddress}}/api/events/demo/product-viewed?distinctId=user-123&productId=sku-42&category=electronics

### Feature flags - check single flag
GET {{PostHogSample.Api_HostAddress}}/api/featureflags/check/new-dashboard?distinctId=user-123

### Feature flags - run experiment
POST {{PostHogSample.Api_HostAddress}}/api/featureflags/experiments/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "distinctId": "user-123",
  "experimentFlagKey": "checkout-experiment"
}

### Errors - demo exception
GET {{PostHogSample.Api_HostAddress}}/api/errors/demo/trigger?distinctId=user-123

### Cohorts - list (requires personal API key)
GET {{PostHogSample.Api_HostAddress}}/api/cohorts?limit=10

### Actions - list (requires personal API key)
GET {{PostHogSample.Api_HostAddress}}/api/actions?limit=10

### Dashboards - list (requires personal API key)
GET {{PostHogSample.Api_HostAddress}}/api/dashboards?limit=10

### Insights - list (requires personal API key)
GET {{PostHogSample.Api_HostAddress}}/api/insights?limit=10
